Peace of mind for the future

Did you know that 60% of people worldwide don’t have a will?

Planning isn’t just an option—it’s a responsibility. Ensuring your legacy is secure means preparing today for tomorrow’s possibilities. By choosing beneficiaries, you create a lasting impact, knowing your loved ones are cared for, and your hard work endures. Protect what matters most. Don’t let your Bitcoin be part of the 60% that’s unprotected.

Easily create a secure Bitcoin legacy plan

We take the complexity and uncertainty out of transferring Bitcoin wealth.

With streamlined security for beneficiary information, Xapo Bank reduces the risks of fraud and technical errors, ensuring a smooth, reliable transfer.

Your wishes are carried out with care, making the process as seamless as possible for you and your loved ones.

Shape your legacy with confidence

Around 20% of all Bitcoin—worth over USD 140 billion—has been lost or inaccessible, mostly because owners didn’t consider their Bitcoin legacy planning.

Now, the power of passing on your legacy is fully in your hands. Thoughtfully choose who will receive your Bitcoin held with us and when by nominating beneficiaries, setting custom percentages, and making easy adjustments to your plan as life evolves.
